ir","incluent"]},{"word":"included","translation":["inclu","inclus","inclûmes","inclues","inclue"]},{"word":"includes","translation":["comporte"]},{"word":"including","translation":["inclusivement","incluyant"]},{"word":"incoherence","translation":["incohérence"]},{"word":"incoherent","translation":["incohérent"]},{"word":"incombustible","translation":["incombustible"]},{"word":"income","translation":["rente","revenu"]},{"word":"incomes","translation":["revenus"]},{"word":"incommensurately","translation":["inadéquat"]},{"word":"incompatibility","translation":["incompatibilité"]},{"word":"incompatible","translation":["inconciliable"]},{"word":"incompetence","translation":["incompétence"]},{"word":"incomprehensible","translation":["inconcevable"]},{"word":"inconsistency","translation":["inconséquence"]},{"word":"inconvenience","translation":["contretemps","inconvénient"]},{"word":"inconvenient","translation":["déplacé","dur","difficile"]},{"word":"incorporate","translation":["incorporent","incorporez","annexer","incorporer"]},{"word":"incorporated","translation":["agrégé","agrégea","incorpora","incorporé","incorporai"]},{"word":"incorporates","translation":["agrége","incorpore"]},{"word":"incorporating","translation":["agrégeant","incorporant"]},{"word":"incorrect","translation":["incorrect","postiche"]},{"word":"increase","translation":["agrandir","accroitre","augmentons","augmentez"]},{"word":"increased","translation":["augmentées","augmenta","augmentés","augmentèrent"]},{"word":"increases","translation":["augmente"]},{"word":"increasing","translation":["augmentant"]},{"word":"increments","translation":["paliers"]},{"word":"incriminate","translation":["incriminent","incriminer","incriminez","incriminons"]},{"word":"incriminated","translation":["incriminai","incriminèrent","incriminâmes","incrimina"]},{"word":"incriminates","translation":["incrimine"]},{"word":"incriminating","translation":["incriminant"]},{"word":"incrustation","translation":["travestissement"]},{"w ety","translation":["gage"]},{"word":"surface","translation":["superficie","surface"]},{"word":"surge","translation":["enflent","enflez","déferlement","enfler","enflons"]},{"word":"surged","translation":["enflées","enflés","enflée","enflèrent","enfla","enflai"]},{"word":"surgeon","translation":["chirurgien"]},{"word":"surgery","translation":["chirurgie"]},{"word":"surges","translation":["enfle"]},{"word":"surgical
